author: Ellen McCutchan
title: No, Joe Exotic doesn't have COVID-19, and other coronavirus misinformation
description: Netflix documentary Tiger King has risen sharply in popularity as coronavirus forces people into lockdown. So it's no surprise that a rumour began that one of its main protagonists has been infected.
content:
Updated 
April 09, 2020 09:13:11
